window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I finally found a piece of my past, but is he who he claims to be?<br> <br> As my powers surge and the fierce love I feel for my mages intensifies, a discovery no one expected is about to change everything.<br> <br> With the Anti Magick Alliance closing in on me, the Bureau convinced I murdered a helpless human, and the Human Extinction League getting ready to unleash their plans on Phoenix Falls, I'll need all the strength I can find to survive.<br> <br> But I'm pretty sure there will be time for some fun along the way....</p> <p><i>Ashes</i> is the third book in The Phoenix Prophecy series. It is a full-length paranormal romance novel with MM and a cliffhanger. Check author's site for TW.</p>"; 
